How it works

1) Absorb

L‑Methylfolate enters the one‑carbon pathway (methylation), supporting healthy folate status without conversion steps.*

2) Activate

With Methyl‑B12 as a co‑factor, methylation supports the natural synthesis of neurotransmitters involved in attention and mood.*

3) Support

Consistent daily use helps maintain a steady nutrient baseline that supports focus, calm, sleep quality and learning routines.*

FAQ

Is it safe for daily use?

L‑methylfolate and methyl‑B12 are active vitamin forms used by the body every day. Neupril is manufactured in GMP‑certified facilities and third‑party tested. Always consult your child’s healthcare provider.

How soon will we notice benefits?

Some families notice subtle changes within 1–2 weeks; most evaluate over 4–8 weeks while keeping a simple progress journal.

Can we use it with other routines or medications?

Many families integrate Neupril with existing supplement or therapy routines. Speak with your pediatrician, particularly if your child uses prescription medications.
